    "description": "\n\nARCUATE ARTERY\n\n\nArcuate artery can refer to:\n\nArcuate artery of the foot\nArcuate arteries of the kidney\nArcuate vessels of uterus\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcuate_artery",
