    "side": "Right",
    "description": "\n\nDORSAL DIGITAL ARTERIES OF FOOT\n\n\nThe dorsal digital arteries of foot are small arteries which supply the toes.\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorsal_digital_arteries_of_foot",
