    "side": "Right",
    "description": "\n\nPROPER PLANTAR DIGITAL ARTERIES\n\n\nThe proper plantar digital arteries are arteries of the foot.\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proper_plantar_digital_arteries",
