    "description": "\n\nLATERAL OCCIPITAL ARTERY (P3)\n\n\nLateral terminal branch of the posterior cerebral artery. \n\nIt is distributed to the basal surface of the occipital lobe and to the posterior part of the temporal lobe.\n\n\n\nFeneis 248.14\n\n\n",
