    "side": "Left",
    "description": "\n\nMEDIAL OCCIPITAL ARTERY (P4)\n\n\nMedial terminal branch of the posterior cerebral artery. \n\nIt goes to the medial surface of the occipital lobe.\n\n\n\nFeneis 248.18\n\n\n",
