    "side": "Left",
    "description": "\n\nDORSAL METATARSAL VEINS\n\n\nThe dorsal metatarsal veins are veins which drain the metatarsus of the foot.\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorsal_metatarsal_veins",
