    "description": "\n\nRIGHT COLIC VEIN\n\n\nThe right colic vein drains the ascending colon, and is a tributary of the superior mesenteric vein. \n\nIt travels with its corresponding artery, the right colic artery.\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right_colic_vein",
