    "side": "Left",
    "description": "\n\nSUPERIOR LABIAL VEIN\n\n\nThe superior labial vein is the vein receiving blood from the upper lip.\n\n\n== External links ==\n\n\n\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superior_labial_vein",
