    "description": "\n\nSUBMENTAL VEIN\n\n\nFollowing the submental artery, the submental vein anastomoses with the sublingual vein and the anterior jugular vein.",
    "function": "Carries blood to facilitate gas, nutrient, and waste exchange across the tissue beds.",
